58:19.329 --> 58:21.247
That's good.

58:21.331 --> 58:23.875
- Yeah!
- Yeah.

58:23.959 --> 58:26.627
Is Lewis okay?
He doesn't normally drink so much.

58:28.380 --> 58:30.298
Yeah, he's totally fine.

58:41.268 --> 58:44.270
Fuller, get the phone.

59:00.454 --> 59:02.538
Hello.

59:02.623 --> 59:05.708
Now I thought
you said there was no girl.

59:05.792 --> 59:09.837
- What?
