59:42.579 --> 59:44.205
- He's watching us!
- Rusty Nail?

59:44.289 --> 59:45.915
- He just called me.
- Who's Rusty Nail?

59:45.999 --> 59:47.083
He called you on the phone?

59:47.167 --> 59:50.127
Yeah, just now. He knew you were
in here. He's watching us!

59:50.212 --> 59:51.420
