01:06:38.661 --> 01:06:41.955
Your heart pounding.

01:06:42.040 --> 01:06:44.416
Face burning hot.

01:06:45.293 --> 01:06:48.337
Now they know what it feels like

01:06:48.421 --> 01:06:51.840
