01:11:30.244 --> 01:11:32.704
Let's go! Go! Go! Go!

01:11:36.376 --> 01:11:38.543
Let's go! Come on!

01:11:55.353 --> 01:11:57.729
Come on!

01:12:01.442 --> 01:12:03.735
Go! Run!

01:12:03.820 --> 01:12:06.613
